div.span: Assertive Logicians are Introverted, Intuitive, Thinking, Judging and Assertive. These thoughtful tacticians love perfecting the details of life, applying creativity and rationality.
Prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Very imaginative and open-minded, focusing on hidden meanings and distant possibilities.
Focuses on objectivity and rationality, putting effectiveness above social harmony.
Decisive, thorough, and highly organized. You value clarity and prefer planning to spontaneity.
Self-assured, even-tempered, and resistant to stress, refusing to worry too much.
